    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example retains the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and structural subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension is upgraded with Bilstein B6 dampers for improved damping profiles without sacrificing streetability. While the finish shows minor cosmetic wear consistent with its 'good' status, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. A mechanically sorted, analog driver's car ready for the canyons.",
