      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday practicality. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, showing only the minor character marks and light stone chips expected from careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, the dashboard remains crack-free, and every electronic feature\u2014from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine delivers smooth, reliable power, a testament to a life of on-time oil changes and preventative care. Recent service includes a fresh set of all-season tires and a comprehensive brake service, ensuring this car is road-trip ready the moment you take the keys. Garage-kept and smoke-free, this vehicle represents an excellent opportunity for a buyer who values mechanical integrity and a clean, honest aesthetic.",
